bilingual.source: Take its photo, and show the photo to the doctors.
bilingual.target: 拍下它的照片，并把照片给医生看。

yingyinNormal.en: Where's his photo? He doesn't like being photographed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的照片呢？他不喜欢拍照。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's take a photo for Teddy Playgroup's album. Say cheese.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们来拍几张照片放到它的相册里。说，茄子。

yingyinNormal.en: You said you'd take back my photo. You promised, Miguel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说过你会把我的照片带回去，米格尔，你答应过我的。

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, Max. There's got to be one photo of kitty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别这样 Max，肯定会有一张猫咪的照片的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, yes, and look, now, you have a photo to remember that heroic day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有张照片记录英勇的一天。

yingyinNormal.en: Gave him a ride. He took that photo of my hand on the stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我送了他一程。当我的手在控制杆上时，他拍这张照片。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Gold, is the man in this surveillance photo Mr. Jim Moody?
yingyinNormal.zh: 戈德先生，监控照片里的那名男子是吉姆·穆迪先生吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I shaved of a couple of inches for the photo. You know the drill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我把房间的照片"修了修"，你们肯定懂的嘛。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I need a diversion. You have a photo of yourself? No. I need one?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我需要分散一下注意力，你有自己的照片吗？没有，要拍一张吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Like, okay, when I look at this photo, I think, I could stand up straighter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如说，当我看到这张照片时，我觉得我可以站得更直一点。

yingyinNormal.en: You took my photo off the ofrenda? It was an accident. How do we send him back?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你把我的照片从祭坛上取下来了？那是个意外。我们怎么送他回去？

yingyinNormal.en: What'd you do, delete your photo? Go. Fine. And don't you slam that door. Oh, man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你做了什么，删掉自己的照片吗？出去。好吧。你敢摔门试试。可恶。

yingyinNormal.en: Come in. Welcome to "The Williamsburg experience." It's bigger than it looks in the photo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请进，欢迎来到"体验威廉斯堡之旅"。房子比照片上看起来大呢。

yingyinNormal.en: When? Don't act surprised. I showed the bellmen a photo. One of them remembers seeing her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么时候? 别假装惊讶，我给门童看过照片，其中一人记得见过她。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I'll show you a photo. Well, I would, but now my phone's not working. Oh, here he is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我给你们看照片，我是想给你们看，但我手机坏了，对了，这里有他。

yingyinNormal.en: I give you my blessing to go home, to put my photo back on the ofrenda, and to never play music again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我给你祝福，让你回家把我的照片放到祭坛上，然后永远不要再碰音乐。

yingyinNormal.en: Miguel, if we help you get his photo, you will return home, no more music. Family comes first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 米格尔，如果我们帮你拿到照片，你就要乖乖回家，不再做音乐梦，永远把家人放在第一。

yingyinNormal.en: You're going after child labor? Seriously? Erik worked four hours a day, five days a week per photo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是想说童工吗？你确定吗？埃里克拍一张照片，每天要工作4小时，一周工作五天。

yingyinNormal.en: I always hoped I'd see her again. That she'd miss me. Maybe put up my photo. But it never happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一直希望能再见她一面，我也希望她会想念我，会把我的照片放上灵台，但我的愿望从没实现过。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a baby sheep. It's me. You are not a baby. It's an old photo when I was a baby. Don't be silly, Suzy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是一只羊宝宝。这是我。你不是宝宝。这是我还是宝宝的时候的一张老照片。别傻了，苏西。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: We're fairly good at judging people based on first impressions, thin slices of experience ranging from a glimpse of a <highlight>photo</highlight> to five-minute interaction.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们相当擅长根据第一印象比如从一张照片的一瞥到五分钟的互动等浅薄的经验片段来判断人。

examination_example.sentence: Facebook, therefore, is a self-enhancer's paradise, where people can share only the most flattering <highlight>photos</highlight>, the cream of their wit, style, beauty, intellect and lifestyles.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，Facebook就成了自我美好者的天堂，人们可以只分享自己最满意的照片，最好的智慧，时尚，美貌，学识和生活方式。

word_usage.usage: photo表“照片”，为可数名词。"拍张照片"用take a photo表达，北美英语常用take a picture。

examination_example.sentence: One of the <highlight>photos</highlight> shows a thin film of clouds above the brilliant blue of the North Atlantic.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在其中一张照片里，北大西洋上方美丽的蓝天高悬着一层薄云。

examination_example.sentence: What has caused the thick clouds in the <highlight>photos</highlight> taken by NASA satellite?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 是什么导致了NASA卫星拍摄的照片中的浓云？

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Frequent stops are made for <highlight>photo</highlight> taking as your guide offers unique facts and history.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你的导游讲解独特的事实和历史时，你可以经常停下来拍照。

examination_example.sentence: About one month after this <highlight>photo</highlight> was taken, I became a new member of the school music club.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大概在这张照片拍摄一个月后，我成为学校音乐俱乐部的一名新成员。

examination_example.sentence: A new collection of <highlight>photos</highlight> brings an unsuccessful Antarctic voyage back to life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一组新的照片使一次失败的南极之旅重现生机。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Before leaving, he gave me a <highlight>photo</highlight> album.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 临走前，他给了我一本相册。

examination_example.sentence: Last month, I got some <highlight>photos</highlight> from the Brazilian girl.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上个月，我从巴西女孩那里得到了一些照片。

examination_example.sentence: Later, we post the <highlight>photos</highlight> onto Weibo or WeChat, waiting to be "liked."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 后来我们把照片发到微博或者微信上，等着被“点赞”。

word_usage.usage: photo表“照片”，为可数名词。"拍张照片"用take a photo表达，北美英语常用take a picture。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 除了可以表示“照片；相片”之外，还可以指图画、图片等，范围较广。
